{"tid":1162104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲人係咪有口話人唔識話自己？","createTime":"2019-05-19T15:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T16:38:23.000Z","uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99ec2124fba20e7c278b51f5e1443cd3347f2aa7","tid":1162104,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"我坐緊巴士，隔離有嗰港女喺度同friend傾電話<br />\n佢話啲人唔識戴耳筒睇片，製造嘈音，嘈住佢搭巴士<br />\n但係自己又喺度大大聲講電話，講哂粗口<br />\n知唔知乜撚嘢叫「己所不欲，勿施於人」？<br />\n自己都唔想遇到嘅事，就咪撚做依啲行為<br />\n剩係識有口話人，冇口話自己<br />\n仲要每句都要加粗口，好撚嘈同好難聽<br />\n唔該你話人之前，控制好自己行為先<br />\n唔係每次一定要同人鬥大聲㗎！<br />\n為人為己，請顧及別人感受！"},{"pid":"7db1229eabf6734c85b5fb36fb78db8674096037","tid":1162104,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"再加一句，喺度嘈撚住我聽歌<br />\n屌你老母<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"1bfcc7842a4b90d6c04a9e1a7d0f81a874575ed9","tid":1162104,"uid":99086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"你咁勁點解唔當面屌佢？"},{"pid":"a45a42075c08347604ad47f14b56dfbf094b0acd","tid":1162104,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bfcc7842a4b90d6c04a9e1a7d0f81a874575ed9","tid":1162104,"uid":99086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"你咁勁點解唔當面屌佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"而家啲人都係網上兇狠，現實碌撚"},{"pid":"adf96e423a2295f4c27a0d4d14a093009fab67df","tid":1162104,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bfcc7842a4b90d6c04a9e1a7d0f81a874575ed9","tid":1162104,"uid":99086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"你咁勁點解唔當面屌佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:10:19.000Z","msg":"同佢講過一次 <br />\n佢話人地嘈住佢，所以要同人地鬥大聲"},{"pid":"837f215afe736ec808f49b80e9c8dbf5b06e170f","tid":1162104,"uid":56940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"佢應該唔敢直接屌<br />\n所以突登大大聲俾嗰個唔戴耳筒嘅人聽"}]}